title: Apple Internal Use Software
description:
This DVD is part of a disc set a friend of mine purchased from an Apple Employee.
The Other DVD is just plain old leopard, there are plenty of those torrents on this site. This is a bunch of software Apple I assume uses on the computers they use in thier office.

This isa .cdr file created on my OSx86 Box, and it works there, so it should work on a real mac too.
